The school really does think of us.

162
00:07:22,799 --> 00:07:24,960
Feeding us veggies and tofu every day.

163
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,599
Just the sight of these makes me sick.

164
00:07:26,599 --> 00:07:28,000
I'd rather have pickles today.

165
00:07:28,071 --> 00:07:29,390
We're not allowed to eat outside.

166
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,719
This is all we get.

167
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:43,229
You gave me the pork chop.

168
00:07:43,230 --> 00:07:44,137
