169
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,440
It's fine. I eat this
at home all the time.

170
00:07:51,799 --> 00:07:52,440
Good?

171
00:07:53,604 --> 00:07:55,382
If you like it,
I'll bring you some tomorrow.

172
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:05,440
Dad,

173
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:07,640
