ten more pork chops for me?

174
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,982
I'll bring them to school.

175
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:10,159
Ten?

176
00:08:10,719 --> 00:08:11,760
Why do you need so many?

177
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:13,440
Mr. Sun tutors me after class,

178
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,880
and the class rep helps me review.

179
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,200
I should treat them.

180
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:17,560
True.

181
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,399
Is ten enough?

182
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,479
I'll make you more.

183
00:08:20,719 --> 00:08:21,279
That's enough.

184
00:08:21,293 --> 00:08:22,830
