miss Shen's pork chops.

190
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,960
They melt in your mouths.

191
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,119
It's amazing.

192
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:35,999
You know what?

193
00:08:35,999 --> 00:08:37,359
Especially for you girls,

194
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,519
we only use

195
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:39,560
lean meat.

196
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:41,080
It won't make you gain weight.

197
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,280
Good?

198
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,320
- Good!
- Good!

199
00:08:45,115 --> 00:08:46,750
If you like it, come again tomorrow.

200
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:47,982
There'll be more tomorrow.

