(Pork Chop Guide)
Read this.

216
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:45,320
Where's the principal, Mr. Hua?

217
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,680
Mr. Sun,

218
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,759
is Shen Minghui from your class?

219
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:51,320
Yes.

220
00:09:51,839 --> 00:09:53,440
This brat disrupted school order.

221
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,080
The canteen is a mess now.

222
00:09:55,999 --> 00:09:56,719
What did he do?

223
00:09:57,115 --> 00:09:59,115
He was giving out free pork chops
in the canteen.

224
00:10:00,719 --> 00:10:01,200
That's it?

225
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:05,879
You came here
to complain to the principal over that?

226
00:10:06,119 --> 00:10:07,400
Listen, Mr. Hua.

227
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:09,440
We senior year teachers are swamped.

228
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:10,990
The homeroom teachers are even busier.

229
00:10:10,999 --> 00:10:11,639
Look.

230
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:13,200
I barely have time to drink water.

231
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,200
Let me tell you this.

232
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,440
His family runs a restaurant.

233
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,080
Their pork chops are really good.

234
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,119
I've had them too.

235
00:10:19,119 --> 00:10:20,719
But there's a problem now.

236
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:23,400
Students come to the canteen

237
00:10:23,759 --> 00:10:25,440
later and later

238
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,440
just for the pork chops.

239
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:28,182
They're missing
the afternoon study hall.

240
00:10:28,182 --> 00:10:29,590
There's this "Pork Chop Guide"

241
00:10:29,599 --> 00:10:30,680
going viral.

242
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,250
It's just one tiny piece of meat,

243
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:33,960
and they treat it like
some kind of panacea.

244
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,879
Does that make sense?

245
00:10:34,999 --> 00:10:36,119
This is a school.

246
00:10:36,119 --> 00:10:37,440
A place to study.

247
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,759
Not to dine out!

248
00:10:38,759 --> 00:10:40,359
Alright. Stop shouting.

249
00:10:40,359 --> 00:10:40,999
I got it.

250
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,800
Alright, I'll handle it.

251
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:53,239
Mr. Pan, you wanted to see me?

252
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:55,639
Mr. Sun,

253
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:57,680
Mr. Pan's phone
has been ringing off the hook.

254
00:10:57,693 --> 00:10:59,710
