about the canteen food.

255
00:10:59,719 --> 00:11:01,080
Today they want pork chops,

256
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,440
tomorrow they'll want hotpot,

257
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,570
and the day after,
they'll demand Alaskan King Crab.

258
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,040
Mr. Pan,

259
00:11:11,359 --> 00:11:13,719
Sheng Minghui must be
dealt with seriously.

260
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:16,160
Giving him a demerit would be too light.

261
00:11:16,479 --> 00:11:17,210
I heard he has been

262
00:11:17,220 --> 00:11:19,471
in high school for five years
and still hasn't graduated.

263
00:11:19,471 --> 00:11:20,893
He's undoubtedly a trouble.

264
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:22,759
We might as well take this chance to...

265
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:23,719
Mr. Hua,

266
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:26,839
